## Verification Plan

### Automated/Tool Verification
- Run `flutter pub get` and verify that shader files compile successfully.
- Check for Dart compiler/analyzer warnings or errors using standard Flutter lint checks.

### Manual Verification
- Run the Flutter app in the web browser (or emulator/physical device if needed) using `flutter run`.
- Drag fingers or cursor to check for fluid trails and swirls reacting in real-time.
- Check responsiveness when scaling parameters via sliders.
- Verify FPS remains close to 60fps.
